author: Justin Harp
title: TV show ratings: Undateable disappoints in Friday return - US TV
text: The all-live season premiere of Undateable debuted low on Friday (October 9), according to Nielsen figures.The sitcom attracted only 0.8 (2.7m) at 8pm and 0.8 (2.42m) at 8.30pm on NBC, while Dateline took 0.9 (4.54m) at 9pm. Â© NBC Universal Last Man Standing and Dr Ken held steady on ABC, averaging 1.3 (6.32m) at 8pm and 1.3 (5.78m) at 8.30pm.Shark Tank garnered 1.5 (5.77m) at 9pm on ABC, before 20/20 scored 1.0 (4.56m) at 10pm.Reign's new season fell a tenth from last year, interesting 0.3 (0.96m) at 8pm on The CW. America's Next Top Model generated 0.3 (0.99m) at 9pm.CBS's The Amazing Race hit 1.1 (5.89m) at 8pm, Hawaii Five-0 reached 1.5 (5.77m) at 9pm, and Blue Bloods earned 1.2 (10.47m) at 10pm.
